For the garage and ramen shop I have done a new aircon model. A Toshiba super inverter. A big aircondition machine, almost twice the size as the once I hade done befor. It was designat using Adobe Illustrator, them photoetched in 0,3mm brass. Then soldered together and then painted. Printed the decals on water decal paper. And finally weathered it with some dry pigments. Stay tuned for the next step on this build.
